INSERT INTO `chat_history` VALUES (1,NULL,'1777573767.464799','kelan ba unang date nag time in and time si jeremy pogi ng am at pm?','Hi, I found Jeremy Pogi\'s first time-in records for you. According to our database, his first AM time-in was at 6:00 AM and his first PM time-in was at 12:00 PM. These are the earliest recorded time-ins for Jeremy. Let me know if you need more information.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:29:29','2026-04-30 18:29:29'),(2,NULL,'1777573905.055776','ano ba nag meron dito sa admin dashboard natin','Kumusta. Sa tingin ko, wala tayong nakitang mga admin users sa dashboard natin. Ang resulta ng query ay wala, kaya\'t hindi natin nakita ang anumang record. Ibig sabihin nito, walang mga account na may role na \'admin\' sa sistema natin. Kung kailangan mo ng tulong sa pag-create ng admin account, pwede kitang tulungan.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:31:46','2026-04-30 18:31:46'),(3,NULL,'1777573917.878061','paano mag logout sa system natin','Upang mag-logout sa system, sundin ang mga sumusunod na hakbang:\n\n1. **Pumunta sa Welcome Page**: Siguraduhin na nasa welcome page ka ng system.\n2. **Hanapin ang Login/Logout Button**: Sa itaas na parte ng page, sa tabi ng navigation bar, mayroong isang button na may label na \"Login\" o \"Logout\".\n3. **I-click ang Logout Button**: Kung ikaw ay nakalogin, ang button ay may label na \"Logout\". I-click mo ito upang simulan ang proseso ng logout.\n4. **Kumpirma ang Logout**: Matapos mong i-click ang logout button, lilitaw ang isang prompt na hihingi ng kumpirma sa iyong logout. Pindutin ang \"OK\" o \"Confirm\" upang tuluyan mong mai-logout.\n5. **Balik sa Welcome Page**: Matapos mong mai-logout, babalik ka sa welcome page ng system.\n\nAdmin Steps:\nKung ikaw ay isang admin, ang proseso ng logout ay pareho sa mga regular na user. Walang karagdagang hakbang na kinakailangan upang mag-logout bilang isang admin.\n\nImportante:\n- Siguraduhin na ikaw ay nakalogout sa system bago mo iwanan ang computer o device upang maiwasan ang anumang potensyal na seguridad na mga isyu.\n- Kung mayroon kang mga hindi na-save na mga gawain o mga dokumento, siguraduhin na mai-save mo ang lahat bago ka mag-logout upang maiwasan ang anumang pagkawala ng data.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:32:00','2026-04-30 18:32:00'),(4,NULL,'1777574092.163992','paano baguhin ang time in and time out ng employee? meron bang mga kailangang documents ?','Kahit na gusto mong baguhin ang time in and time out ng isang empleyado, hindi natin nakita ang anumang record sa ating database. Ibig sabihin nito, wala tayong mga dokumento o record na makikita para sa empleyadong ito. Kung gusto mo talagang magbaguhin ng oras, maaari mong simulan ang proseso ng pagpapakita ng mga kailangang dokumento, pero sa ngayon, wala tayong nakikitang mga detalye. Pakisubukan na makipag-ugnay sa ating HR department para sa karagdagang impormasyon.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:34:54','2026-04-30 18:34:54'),(5,1,'1777574197.276953','Test: How do I register a new employee?','To register a new employee, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the admin portal**: First, you need to log in to the admin portal using your credentials. You can do this by clicking on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page.\n2. **Navigate to the Personnel section**: After logging in, navigate to the Personnel section. You can do this by clicking on the \"Personnel\" link in the top navigation bar.\n3. **Click on the \"Stats Grid\" card**: On the Personnel page, you will see a \"Stats Grid\" section. Click on the card that displays the total number of personnel.\n4. **Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button**: Unfortunately, the provided code does not explicitly show the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button. However, based on the context, it is likely that you will find this button on the Personnel page or on a related page.\n\n**Employee Registration Wizard:**\n\n1. **Step 1: Personal details**: Fill in the employee\'s personal details, such as name, address, and contact information. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n2. **Step 2: Account details**: Fill in the employee\'s account details, such as username and password. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n3. **Step 3: Employment details**: Fill in the employee\'s employment details, such as job title, department, and employment date. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n4. **Step 4: Contact details**: Fill in the employee\'s contact details, such as phone number and email address. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n5. **Step 5: Gov IDs**: Fill in the employee\'s government-issued IDs, such as ID number and expiration date. Click \"Next\" to proceed to the next step.\n6. **Step 6: Review and submit**: Review all the details you have entered and submit the registration form.\n\n**Validation rules:**\n\n* Please note that some fields may be required or have specific validation rules, such as password strength or email format. Make sure to fill in all the required fields and follow the validation rules to successfully register a new employee.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to register a new employee. If you encounter any issues or have further questions, please don\'t hesitate to ask.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:36:39','2026-04-30 18:36:39'),(7,NULL,'1777574209.690193','Test: What is my attendance?','Database error: 1242 (21000): Subquery returns more than 1 row','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 18:36:50','2026-04-30 18:36:50'),(8,NULL,'1777574381.423025','how to register new employee?','To register a new employee, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the admin dashboard**: First, make sure you are logged in to the admin dashboard with the correct credentials.\n2. **Navigate to the personnel page**: Click on the \"Personnel\" tab or menu item to access the personnel management page.\n3. **Click on the \"Add New Employee\" button**: Look for a button that says \"Add New Employee\" or \"Register New Employee\" and click on it.\n4. **Fill in the employee details**: A form will appear where you need to fill in the employee\'s details, such as:\n	* First name\n	* Last name\n	* Email address\n	* Job title\n	* Department\n	* Date of birth\n	* Contact information (phone number, address, etc.)\n5. **Upload required documents**: You may need to upload required documents, such as:\n	* ID proof (passport, driver\'s license, etc.)\n	* Resume or CV\n	* Other relevant documents\n6. **Set up employee credentials**: Create a username and password for the new employee, or generate a default password that the employee can change later.\n7. **Save the employee details**: Once you have filled in all the required fields, click on the \"Save\" or \"Register\" button to create the new employee account.\n8. **Verify employee information**: Review the employee\'s information to ensure everything is accurate and complete.\n\n**Validation rules:**\n\n* Make sure to fill in all required fields, as indicated by asterisks (*) or other visual cues.\n* Ensure that the email address is unique and not already in use by another employee.\n* Verify that the uploaded documents are in the correct format (e.g., PDF, JPEG, etc.) and meet the required specifications.\n\n**What happens next:**\n\n* The new employee will receive an email with their login credentials and a link to reset their password.\n* The employee will be able to log in to the system and access their profile, where they can update their information and change their password.\n* The admin will be able to view the new employee\'s profile and manage their access to different features and modules within the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\chatbot\\\\adminChatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\"]','2026-04-30 18:39:43','2026-04-30 18:39:43'),(9,NULL,'1777574784.911362','Find administrator','I\'ve searched our database for an administrator, but unfortunately, no results were found. It looks like there are no users with the \'admin\' role in our system. If you\'re trying to get in touch with someone for assistance, I\'d be happy to help you explore other options. Please let me know how I can further assist you.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 18:46:26','2026-04-30 18:46:26'),(10,NULL,'1777575883.778092','How many people work here?','To find out how many people work in your organization, you can follow these steps:\n\n**Step 1: Access the Chatbot**\nGo to the chatbot interface, usually found on the main page or a dedicated chat window. You can also access it through the admin dashboard.\n\n**Step 2: Type Your Question**\nIn the chat window, type your question: \"How many people work here?\" You can also use variations of this question, such as \"What is the total number of employees?\" or \"How many staff members do we have?\"\n\n**Step 3: Send Your Question**\nClick the \"Send\" button or press Enter to submit your question to the chatbot.\n\n**Step 4: View the Response**\nThe chatbot will process your question and provide a response. If your question is valid, the chatbot will display the total number of employees in your organization.\n\n**Step 5: Verify the Information (Optional)**\nIf you want to verify the information, you can access the admin dashboard and navigate to the \"Departments\" or \"Employees\" section. There, you can find the total number of employees listed.\n\n**Admin Steps:**\nIf you are an admin, you can also follow these steps to find the total number of employees:\n\n1. Log in to the admin dashboard.\n2. Navigate to the \"Departments\" or \"Employees\" section.\n3. Look for the \"Total Personnel\" or \"Total Employees\" field, which displays the total number of employees in your organization.\n\nNote: The chatbot uses natural language processing to understand your question, so you can ask your question in a conversational tone. The chatbot will do its best to provide an accurate response based on the data available in the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\test-chatbot.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\departments\\\\adminDepartments.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Models\\\\Employee.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:04:45','2026-04-30 19:04:45'),(11,NULL,'1777575928.876985','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can follow these steps:\n\n**Step 1: Login to the System**\nFirst, you need to log in to the system. Click on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page and enter your email and password. If you don\'t have an account, you can sign up by clicking on the \"Signup\" button.\n\n**Step 2: Access the Admin Dashboard**\nAfter logging in, you will be redirected to the admin dashboard. If you are an admin user, you will see a dashboard with various options.\n\n**Admin Steps:**\nTo access the employee registration data, follow these steps:\n\n**Step 3: Click on the \"Personnel\" Option**\nOn the admin dashboard, click on the \"Personnel\" option. This will take you to a page where you can manage employee data.\n\n**Step 4: Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\"**\nOn the personnel page, click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" option. This will take you to a wizard that guides you through the employee registration process.\n\n**Step 5: Complete the Wizard**\nHowever, since you want to know how many employees are registered, you don\'t need to complete the wizard. Instead, look for a button or link that says \"View Registered Employees\" or \"Employee List\".\n\n**Step 6: View the Employee List**\nClick on the \"View Registered Employees\" or \"Employee List\" button. This will take you to a page that displays a list of all registered employees.\n\n**Step 7: Check the Employee Count**\nOn the employee list page, you can see the total number of employees registered in the system. You can also use the search or filter options to narrow down the list and get the count of employees based on specific criteria.\n\nAlternatively, you can also use the chatbot feature to ask the question \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\" (how many employees are registered in the system?). The chatbot will respond with the total number of registered employees.\n\nNote: The exact steps may vary depending on the system\'s configuration and the user\'s role. These steps are based on the provided codebase and may not match the actual system\'s workflow.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:05:31','2026-04-30 19:05:31'),(12,1,'1777576046.725553','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Login to the system**: First, you need to log in to the system using your valid credentials. Click on the \"Login\" button on the top right corner of the page and enter your email and password. If you don\'t have an account, you can sign up by clicking on the \"Signup\" button.\n\n2. **Access the Admin Dashboard**: After logging in, if you are an admin, you will be redirected to the admin dashboard. If you are not an admin, you may not have access to the employee registration data.\n\n3. **Admin steps:** As an admin, you can follow these steps:\n    * Click on the \"Employee Registration Wizard\" button or navigate to the employee management section.\n    * Look for a button or link that says \"View All Employees\" or \"Employee List\".\n    * Click on this button to view the list of all registered employees.\n\n4. **View Employee List**: Once you are on the employee list page, you can see the total number of employees registered in the system. This information is usually displayed at the top of the page or in a sidebar.\n\n5. **Use the Chatbot (Alternative Method)**: If you are not an admin or do not have access to the admin dashboard, you can use the chatbot feature to find out how many employees are registered in the system.\n    * Click on the chatbot icon or button on the page.\n    * Type a message in the chat window, such as \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\" (how many employees are registered in the system?).\n    * The chatbot will respond with the total number of employees registered in the system.\n\nNote: The chatbot may ask follow-up questions to clarify your query or provide additional information. Please respond accordingly to get the desired result.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:28','2026-04-30 19:07:28'),(13,1,'1777576067.052454','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, you can use the chatbot feature. Here\'s a step-by-step guide:\n\n1. **Go to the website**: Open the Municipal Government of Pagsanjan, Laguna website.\n2. **Click on the chat icon**: Look for the chat icon on the website, usually found at the bottom right corner of the page.\n3. **Type your question**: In the chat window, type your question in Filipino: \"ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?\"\n4. **Send the message**: Click the send button or press enter to send your question to the chatbot.\n5. **Wait for the response**: The chatbot will process your question and provide a response. If your question is valid, the chatbot will provide the total number of registered employees in the system.\n6. **View the response**: The chatbot will display the response in the chat window, which should include the total number of registered employees.\n\nNote: The chatbot uses query expansion synonyms, which means it can understand similar phrases or words related to your question. For example, you can also ask \"How many employees are registered in the system?\" or \"What is the total number of employees in the system?\" and the chatbot should still provide the correct response.\n\n**Validation rules**: Please note that the chatbot has validation rules in place to ensure that the question is valid and relevant to the system. If your question is not valid, the chatbot will provide a follow-up question or a message indicating that it cannot understand your question.\n\n**Admin steps**: If you are an admin user, you may have additional options to view the total number of registered employees in the system. To do this:\n\n1. **Log in to the admin dashboard**: Go to the admin login page and enter your credentials.\n2. **Navigate to the employee management page**: Look for the employee management page or section in the admin dashboard.\n3. **View the employee list**: The employee list should display the total number of registered employees in the system.\n\nPlease note that admin access is restricted to authorized personnel only.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\ChatbotController.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\modals\\\\employeeWizardComplete.blade.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:49','2026-04-30 19:07:49'),(14,1,'1777576071.142447','How many employees are registered in the system?','To find out how many employees are registered in the system, follow these steps:\n\n**Admin steps:**\n\n1. **Log in to the system**: Go to the login page and enter your admin credentials (email and password). Click the \"Login\" button to access the dashboard.\n2. **Navigate to the Personnel page**: Once logged in, click on the \"Personnel\" link in the navigation menu. This will take you to the admin personnel page.\n3. **View the Total Personnel stat**: On the personnel page, look for the \"Total Personnel\" stat card. This card displays the total number of employees registered in the system.\n4. **Check the stat value**: The stat value will display the total number of employees. This is the answer to your question.\n\nAlternatively, if you want to view more detailed information about the employees:\n\n1. **Click on the stat card**: Click on the \"Total Personnel\" stat card to view more detailed information about the employees.\n2. **View the employee list**: This will take you to a page that lists all the employees registered in the system. You can scroll through the list to see the total number of employees.\n\nThat\'s it! By following these steps, you should be able to find out how many employees are registered in the system.','system','[\"What happens after that?\", \"Where do I find that option?\", \"What if I need to...?\"]','[\"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\themeSettings\\\\adminThemeSettings.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\welcome.blade.php\", \"resources\\\\views\\\\admin\\\\personnel\\\\adminPersonnel.blade.php\", \"app\\\\Http\\\\Controllers\\\\AttendanceController.php\", \"routes\\\\web.php\"]','2026-04-30 19:07:52','2026-04-30 19:07:52'),(15,1,'1777576074.423742','How many employees are there?','There are 11 employees in total, according to our database. I\'ve just run a quick query to get the latest count, and it looks like our team is made up of 11 individuals. If you need more information about our employees, such as their roles or departments, I\'d be happy to help with that as well. Let me know how I can assist you further.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 19:07:55','2026-04-30 19:07:55'),(16,1,'1777576109.956546','ilan ang empleyado na registerdito sa sytem?','Kumusta. Ayon sa aming mga record, may 11 na empleyado na nakarehistro sa sistema. Ito ay batay sa resulta ng pagtatanong sa database namin. Kaya, may kabuuang 11 na mga empleyado na nakalista sa ating sistema.','database','[\"Show me more details\", \"Filter by a different criteria\", \"How many total records are there?\"]',NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:32','2026-04-30 19:08:32'),(17,1,'1777576114.208199','How many employees are registered in the system?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:34','2026-04-30 19:08:34'),(18,1,'1777576116.712889','How many employees are there?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:08:37','2026-04-30 19:08:37'),(19,1,'1777576147.046105','How many employees are there?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:09:07','2026-04-30 19:09:07'),(20,NULL,'1777576320.244587','ilan ang employees natin?','Sorry, an error occurred. Please try again.','error',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-30 19:12:02','2026-04-30 19:12:02');
